name: Zuikaku
acquisitionMethod: Drop, Construction and Event Shop in Visitors Dyed in Red

1.name: Default
1.description: Second ship of the Shoukaku Class aircraft carriers-Zuikaku

limitBreak.tier1: Number of Dive Bombers +1 / All Plane Efficiency +3%
limitBreak.tier2: Hangar Capacity +1 / Number of Torpedo Bombers +1 / All Plane Efficiency +5%
limitBreak.tier3: Number of All Planes +1 / All Plane Efficiency +7%

1.name: Gokkousen (Zuikaku)
1.description: When paired with Shoukaku, increase Air Power by 8% (20%) and receive 8% (20%) less damage.

2.name: Crane's Endeavor
2.description: When providing air support, permanently increase the next air strike damage by 8% (20%). Can be stacked 3 times.

1.chinese: 翔鹤级航空母舰二番舰—瑞鹤
1.chineseTL: Second ship of the Shoukaku Class aircraft carriers-Zuikaku.

2.chinese: 我是五航战的瑞鹤！嘛，虽然也去过一航战就是啦。和姐姐一同，在前辈们华丽丽地退场后成为了重樱仅存的精锐航母。虽然还有一些后辈，可遗憾的是没发挥什么作用就都去追随一航战们了。参与击沉过列克星敦和大黄蜂，也重伤过企业，不过——灰色幽灵那家伙，说不定、不，是肯定比我更幸运吧！最后经列克星敦之手谢幕，也算是宿命和因果的轮回吧，不过和前辈们不同，在谢幕之前——我可是好好地把自己最后的任务完成了哟！
2.chineseTL: I am Zuikaku from the Fifth Carrier Division!...Ok fine, I was also a part of the First Carrier Division. Together with sister, after our predecessors made their magnificent exit, we became the last two elite carriers of the Sakura Empire. Even though we did have some juniors, unfortunately they did not accomplish much before suffering the same fate as the First Carrier Division. I participated in the sinking of Lexington and Hornet, and severely damaged Enterprise, but the Grey Ghost is probably, no, definitely more lucky than me!Finally, my performance was ended by Lexington, maybe this is karma. But unlike my predecessors, before I sunk, I splendidly completed my final mission!
2.japanese: 私は五航戦の瑞鶴よ！姉と一緒に先輩たちが沈んだあと重桜陣営最後の精鋭空母として頑張って、レキシントンさんとホーネット、エンタープライズ－－そう、私よりも、幸運な、あの「グレイゴースト」とも戦った！最後は沈んじゃったけど、全力を尽くしたから、悔いはないわ！
2.japaneseTL: I'm the Fifth Carrier Division's Zuikaku! After our seniors sank, my sister and I did our best as the remaining elite aircraft carriers in the Sakura Empire. Against Lexington, Hornet, Enterprise... That's right, I went up against that "Grey Ghost" who had much greater luck than me! Even though I sank in the end, I have no regrets as I've done all that I could.

3.chinese: 我是重樱航空战队最后的精锐——瑞鹤！不过……指挥官，只有在翔鹤姐身边我才能发挥出全部的战斗力唷
3.chineseTL: I am Sakura Empire Carrier Divisions' last elite, Zuikaku! However, I can only be at my best when I am with my sister Shoukaku, commander.
3.japanese: 重桜航空戦隊所属、かつての大戦最後の精鋭空母--瑞鶴よ！まあ、翔鶴姉がいてくれた方が私の力を最大限に発揮できるの。というわけで、よろしく頼むわ
3.japaneseTL: From the Sakura Empire's carrier division, their last elite fleet carrier in the Great War, Zuikaku! Well, I can only utilize my full power when my sister, Shoukaku, is around. That said, it's a pleasure to meet you!

4.chinese: 今天要去哪里？珍珠港还是珊瑚海？
4.chineseTL: Where are we headed today? Pearl Harbour or the Coral Sea?
4.japanese: 今日はどっち？真珠湾？それとも珊瑚海？
4.japaneseTL: Where are we going today? Pearl Harbour? Or perhaps the Coral Sea?

5.chinese: 真想和她单独决斗一次啊，那个灰色幽灵——
5.chineseTL: I really want to duel the Grey Ghost once.
5.japanese: 一対一で本気勝負をしたいな…「グレイゴースト」！
5.japaneseTL: I want to have an all-out one-on-one against the "Grey Ghost "!

6.chinese: 现在这样别扭的翔鹤姐也很可爱！
6.chineseTL: The embarrassed Shoukaku is also very cute!
6.japanese: 拗ねてる翔鶴姉も可愛いよ！
6.japaneseTL: Shoukaku's cute even when she's pouting!

7.chinese: 直到最后都坚持到底，这才是所谓的“精锐”！
7.chineseTL: Perseverance until the very end, that is what it means to be "elite"!
7.japanese: 最後の最後まで戦う…これこそ「精鋭」よ！
7.japaneseTL: To keep fighting right to the very end... That's what it means to be "elite"!

8.chinese: 等等，灰色幽灵，不要赢了就跑！再、再来一次，这次我一定——
8.chineseTL: Wait up, Grey Ghost, do not leave immediately after you win! One more time, this time I will definitely...
8.japanese: 待て！「グレイゴースト」！勝ち逃げは許さないわよ！も、もう一回だけ勝負だ－！今度こそ絶対勝ってやる―！
8.japaneseTL: Wait! "Grey Ghost"! I won't let you leave right after you win! O-one more round! I'll definitely win this time!

9.chinese: 我最讨厌的食物？当然是火鸡咯
9.chineseTL: My least favourite food? Of course it is turkey.
9.japanese: 嫌いな食べ物？七面鳥よ！
9.japaneseTL: Any foods I hate? Turkey, of course!

10.chinese: 指挥官，翔鹤姐的更大更软唷
10.chineseTL: Commander, Shoukaku's are larger and softer.
10.japanese: 指揮官？翔鶴姉のほうがもっと大きくて柔らかいんだよ？
10.japaneseTL: Commander? Shoukaku's are much larger and softer, you know?

11.chinese: 到休息时间了？指挥官，也来尝尝翔鹤姐的手艺吧，嚼嚼～
11.chineseTL: It's break time? Commander, come and try Shoukaku's cooking together with me.
11.japanese: もう休憩なの？あ、翔鶴姉の作った料理、指揮官も食べてみてよ！ほら！（もぐもぐ）
11.japaneseTL: Is it break-time? Commander, try out some of the food Shoukaku's made. Here! (chewing)

12.chinese: 这样、局势应该会稍稍好转一些吧
12.chineseTL: Now, the situation should slightly take a turn for the better.
12.japanese: これで少しは戦局も少し好転するはず…だよね…
12.japaneseTL: With this, the situation should change slightly for the better...

13.chinese: 那么，是好消息？还是坏消息？
13.chineseTL: So? Is it good news or bad news?
13.japanese: で、グッドニュース？バッドニュース？
13.japaneseTL: So, was it good news, or bad news?

14.chinese: 好好整备一下吧——不过，可不能耽误战机！
14.chineseTL: Let's thoroughly service the plane, but we cannot miss the opportunity to strike!
14.japanese: 整備はちゃんと行うようお願いするね－－あ、でも戦機を逃してはダメよ！
14.japaneseTL: I'll need you to perform some maintenance for me... Ahh, don't forget about the planes as well!

15.chinese: 如果能有更多的舰载机……
15.chineseTL: If I could have more planes...
15.japanese: もっと艦載機があれば…！
15.japaneseTL: If I just had more planes...!

16.chinese: 前辈也好、幽灵也好——作为理想型航空母舰，无论和谁比都不会输！
16.chineseTL: Whether it is my predecessors, or the Ghost, as an ideal aircraft carrier, I will never lose!
16.japanese: 完成されし空母として、先輩たちにも「グレイゴースト」にも、絶対負けないわ！
16.japaneseTL: As a perfected aircraft carrier, I definitely won't lose to those seniors or the "Grey Ghost"!

17.chinese: 与像下饺子一样茫茫多的敌舰战斗——我早已习惯了！
17.chineseTL: I am already used to fighting a large number of enemy ships like this!
17.japanese: 次から次へと出て来る敵－こんなのもう慣れっこだからね！
17.japaneseTL: For enemies to come endlessly... I'm already used to it!

18.japanese: 幸運艦の瑞鶴なんだから！
18.japaneseTL: It's because I'm the lucky ship, Zuikaku!

19.chinese: 又要与大炮巨舰……一同消亡了吗……
19.chineseTL: Am I going to perish again?
19.japaneseTL: Am I... going to sink once more...

20.chineseTL: As long as sister is by my side!
20.japanese: お姉ちゃんさえいれば！
20.japaneseTL: As long as my sister's here...!

21.japanese: 姉ちゃん…翔鶴姉は大丈夫！？

22.chinese: 指挥官，你想体验一下——马里亚纳海战时我的心情吗？
22.chineseTL: Commader, do you want to experience the same feeling I was having back in the Mariana Sea Battle?
22.japanese: 指揮官てさあ、マリアナ海戦の私の気持ちを体験したいの？
22.japaneseTL: Hey Commander, do you want to experience what I had felt in the Marianas naval battle?

23.chinese: 呜哇，前辈也好后辈也好，都很让人头痛呢
23.chineseTL: No matter it is my senior or my junior, dealing with they are all so troublesome.
23.japanese: あっちゃ－先輩も後輩もちょっと面倒くさいよね…
23.japaneseTL: Aw crud... Seniors and juniors, they're all such a pain...

24.chinese: 我的命运一直和列克星敦纠缠再一起......啊，指挥官，这句话不要告诉萨拉小姐，我可拿她没辙......
24.chineseTL: My fate seem to be entwined with Lexington... Ah, commander, please do not tell miss Sara that, I cannot deal with her.
24.japanese: そう言えば私って昔レキシントンさんとずっとつるんでたんだよね……あ！指揮官、今のはサラトガさんにだけは言わないでね！私、あのコだけすっごく苦手だよ……
24.japaneseTL: Come to think of it, I used to hang out with Lexington in the past... Ahh! Commander, don't let Saratoga know about what I just said! I really can't handle that girl...

25.chinese: 心情烦乱，不知道该做什么的时候就去训练吧！迟早有一天，我要追上那个“幽灵”！
25.chineseTL: Feeling troubled, and lost? Let's go do some training! I will catch up with that "Ghost", eventually!
25.japanese: イラッとする時や、何すればいいか分からない時はいつも訓練に行っているのよ！そう！私、いつか強くなって、絶対あの「グレイゴースト」を追い抜くんだから！
25.japaneseTL: Whenever I'm irritated or don't know what to do, I always go for some training! That's right, I'll definitely get stronger and catch up to that "Grey Ghost" one day!

26.chinese: 指挥官给我的感觉和翔鹤姐有点像呢......哎、哎？不是啦！我没有把指挥官当初姐姐啦！
26.chineseTL: Commander is giving me a similar feeling as with Shoukaku... eh? No way! I did not mistook Commander for my sister!
26.japanese: 指揮官って、ちょっと翔鶴姉と似てるよね……あ、あれ？違うよ！指揮官をお姉ちゃん扱いしてないってば！
26.japaneseTL: Commander, you're kinda like Shoukaku... H-huh? That's not it! I'm not treating you as my sister!

27.chinese: 哎、哎！这、这代表的是......我、我没有想错吧！？那、那个......从今以后，请多多指教了，亲、亲爱的！呜哇呜哇！翔鹤姐在叫我！
27.chineseTL: Aaah! This, this means... I'm not misinterpreting this, am I? Then, then... from now on, I look forward to working together with you, dar, darling! *embarrassed screeching* Shoukaku is calling me!
27.japanese: え、えええ！？こ、これって……勘違いしていないよね！？そ、その……これからよ、よろしくお願いします…ね？あ、ああ、あなた……わあああ！翔鶴姉が呼んでるよ！！
27.japaneseTL: H-Huh!? T-this is... I'm not misunderstanding anything here, right!? Umm... From now on, I'll be in your care... D-dear... Wahhh! Shoukaku's calling me!

28.chinese: （翔鹤）只要有姐姐在身边，我就无所畏惧！
28.chineseTL: (Shoukaku) As long as sis is by my side, I am fearless!
28.japanese: （翔鶴）翔鶴姉さえいればもう何も怖くない！
28.japaneseTL: (Shoukaku) As long as Shoukaku's by my side, I'm not afraid of anything!

29.chinese: （菲尼克斯）不知为何，就是觉得你很讨厌……
29.chineseTL: (Phoenix) I don't know why, but I just find you very detestable.
29.japanese: （レキシントン）まだ引き分けよ！次で勝負を決めるわよ！
29.japaneseTL: (Lexington) Now it's even! The next round will decide the winner!

30.chineseTL: (Lexington) Score: one all. Third round, start!
30.japanese: （サラトガ）うわ！？サラトガさんいつの間に……！？
30.japaneseTL: (Saratoga) Uwah!? When did Saratoga get here...!?

31.chinese: （萨拉托加）呜哇，一不留神就跑到了我的身边！
31.chineseTL: (Saratoga) Ah! How did you suddenly appear beside me!
31.japanese: （エンタープライズ）「グレイゴースト」と一緒に戦えるなんて…！
31.japaneseTL: (Enterprise) Why am I fighting alongside the "Grey Ghost"...!

32.chinese: （企业）真没想到能和那个“灰色幽灵”并肩战斗！
32.chineseTL: (Enterprise) Never thought that I would be able to fight with that "Grey Ghost" together!
32.japanese: （フェニックス）理由はわからないけど、あんたのことが気に入らないね…
32.japaneseTL: (Phoenix) I don't know why, but I don't really like you...

33.japanese: チョコレートなんて贈ったことないから何を言えばいいかわからないよね……まあとにかく、指揮官、いつもお疲れ様！これからも私たち五航戦に期待してねっ！

34.japanese: 「指揮官、いつもお疲れ様！はい！」…ってこんな感じで渡していいんだっけ？あっ、それとも…「私の気持ちを受け取ってください！///」こ、この感じのほうがいい、かな…？
